subject: Welcome to Turing Email!
html_part:
TURING WELCOME

Welcome, to the Turing email client!

The Turing email client has been designed to enhance your email experience and provide a product that helps you manage the growing demands of modern email communication.

Our client is packed with features to help you do what you want and need to do. Here are some of the features you can enjoy using the Turing email client:

  • An inbox cleaner that files away unimportant emails from your inbox.
  • List subscriptions management through which you can view all lists you are subscribed to and unsubscribe from them.
  • Email tracking that works on a per recipient basis.
  • Email snooze to archive an email and then return it to the inbox after a set period of time.
  • Schedule email send for a specific time in the future.
  • Various analytics reports for understanding your email. These reports cover attachments, email volume, email folders, lists, threads and top contacts.
  • A morning email report highlighting important emails that haven’t been replied to and some other categories of email.
  • Inbox pause to prevent new emails from being loaded for a while.
  • An email context side panel that shows social data and email statistics relevant to the person you’re emailing.
  • Bounceback reminders for emails that haven’t been replied to within a specific time.
  • Quick replies so that you can fire off a preset short response to someone.
  • Email rules and inbox cleaning rules for configuring email filtering and inbox cleaning respectively.
  • Quick compose options & email templates for more quickly composing emails.
  • An email bankruptcy button to totally delete everything in your inbox.

Thank you for signing up for the Turing email client. We will send you an email once your account has been prepared!
Turing Technology, Inc. - all rights reserved 2014 ©

snippet: Hi ruby Tips to get the most out of Gmail Bring your contacts and mail into Gmail On your computer,
subject: Three tips to get the most out of Gmail
html_part:
Hi ruby

Tips to get the most out of Gmail

Bring your contacts and mail into Gmail

On your computer, you can copy your contacts and emails from your old email account to make the transition to Gmail even better. Learn how.
Find what you need fast

With the power of Google Search right in your inbox, it's easy to sort your email. Find what you're looking for with predictions based on email content, past searches and contacts.
Much more than email

You can send text messages and make video calls with Hangouts right from Gmail. To use this feature on mobile, download the Hangouts app for Android and Apple devices.


Happy emailing,
The Gmail Team
© 2015 Google Inc. 1600 Amphitheatre Parkway, Mountain View, CA 94043

snippet: Hi ruby Gmail's inbox puts you in control Inbox video Meet the inbox Gmail's inbox sorts your
subject: Stay more organized with Gmail's inbox
html_part:
Hi ruby

Gmail's inbox puts you in control

Meet the inbox

Gmail's inbox sorts your email into categories so you can see what's new at a glance, decide which emails you want to read when and view similar types of emails together. Watch the video
Choose your categories

The Social and Promotions categories are on by default. Add categories like Updates and Forums or remove categories to have those emails show up in your Primary inbox. Learn how to choose categories
Customize your inbox

If you see a message you want in a different category, you can move it there. On mobile devices, you can even choose which categories create a notification. More customization tips



To learn more about Gmail's inbox, check out the help center or watch the video.


Happy emailing,
The Gmail Team
© 2015 Google Inc. 1600 Amphitheatre Parkway, Mountain View, CA 94043
